{"tid":663243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔公平﹗] 中興通訊:美國銷售禁令處罰過重","createTime":"2018-05-13T06:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T04:14:58.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e93a51c8c297225a53acabe91c0125ccdbf0fce1","tid":663243,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:37:24.000Z","msg":"中興通訊:美國銷售禁令處罰過重<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1841848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1841848&d=I4UYGyOFC9GC9oh4YvWiipWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6829d310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1841848</a><br />\n<br />\n據《華爾街日報》報道，中興通訊(00763)向美國有關部門表示，其<span style=\"color: red;\">未能遵守與美國政府達成的和解協議，是因為內控失誤，而非系統性欺騙，認為美國作出的銷售禁令處罰過重。</span><br />\n<br />\n報道稱，中美可能將在下一輪談判中，繼續就中興事件進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部在上月以中興對涉及歷史出口管制違規行為的某些員工，未及時扣減獎金和發出懲戒信，並在2016年11月30日和2017年7月20日提交給美國政府的兩份函件中作出虛假陳述為由，決定禁止美國公司向中興銷售零部件等長達7年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dffb657ab84a0511958f577570e5af5ed284a0","tid":663243,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ba6c19db06811035383b71c47f8a38b4d567d6","tid":663243,"uid":75326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:43:53.000Z","msg":"中興再咁樣落去，就對唔住要準備為祖國&quot;<strong>亮劍</strong>&quot;嘅同胞了!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7958c477dffb8acfe71cc38f64b0ecbca3adf657","tid":663243,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},